{"title_page": "\u00dcsk\u00fcdar", "text_new": "{{About|the district of Istanbul|the ferry|SS \u00dcsk\u00fcdar|the ghost town|Chrysopolis, California}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2019}}\n\n{{More citations needed|date=April 2007}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n|name              = \u00dcsk\u00fcdar\n|official_name     = Municipality of \u00dcsk\u00fcdar\n|native_name       = \u00dcsk\u00fcdar Belediyesi\n|native_name_lang  = tr\n|other_name        = \n|settlement_type   = \n<!-- images, nickname, motto --->\n|image_skyline     = Maiden tower.JPG\n|imagesize         = 250px\n|image_alt         = A tower on a small island, with a ship nearby\n|image_caption     = [[Maiden's Tower]] ({{lang|tr|K\u0131z Kulesi}}) off the coast of \u00dcsk\u00fcdar in Istanbul \n|image_flag        = \n|flag_size         = \n|flag_alt          = \n|flag_link         =\n|image_seal        = \n|seal_size         = \n|seal_alt          = \n|seal_link         = \n|image_shield      = \n|shield_size       = \n|shield_alt        = \n|shield_link       = \n|link = \n|nickname          = \n|motto             = \n<!-- maps and coordinates ------>\n|image_map         = Istanbul location \u00dcsk\u00fcdar.svg\n|mapsize           = \n|map_alt           = \n|map_caption       = \n|image_map1        = \n|mapsize1          = \n|map_alt1          = \n|map_caption1      = \n|image_dot_map     = \n|dot_mapsize       = \n|dot_map_base_alt  = \n|dot_map_alt       = \n|dot_map_caption   = \n|dot_x = |dot_y    = \n|pushpin_map       = Turkey\n|pushpin_label_position  = <!-- position of the pushpin label: left, right, top, bottom, none -->\n|pushpin_map_alt   = \n|pushpin_mapsize   = \n|pushpin_map_caption =  \n|pushpin_map1      = \n|pushpin_label_position1 = \n|pushpin_map_alt1  = \n|pushpin_mapsize1  = \n|pushpin_map_caption1= \n|coordinates       = {{coord|41|1|26.36|N|29|0|59.48|E|display=inline}}\n|coor_pinpoint     = Municipal Building\n|coordinates_footnotes = <!-- for references: use <ref> tags -->\n<!-- lo