amagaluru\n\n|-\n| [[Mullayanagiri]]\n| Chikkamagaluru\n\n|-\n| [[Nandi Hills, India|Nandi Hills]]\n| Chikkaballapur\n\n|-\n| [[Pushpagiri (mountain)|Pushpagiri]]\n| Dakshina Kannada, Hassan and Kodagu\n\n|-\n| [[Sakleshpur]]\n| Hassan\n\n|-\n| [[Sirsi, Karnataka|Sirsi]]\n| Uttara Kannada\n\n|-\n| [[Somwarpet]]\n| Kodagu\n\n|-\n| [[Skandagiri]]\n| Chikkaballapura\n\n|-\n| [[Virajpet]]\n| Kodagu\n\n|}\n\n==Kerala==\n\n[[File:Munnar hillstation kerala.jpg|thumb|[[Munnar]], Kerala]]\n[[File:Boat similar to the one involved.JPG|thumb|[[Thekkady]], [[Kerala]]]]\n[[File:Hills Vagamon.jpg|thumb|right|Rolling meadows of [[Vagamon]], [[Kerala]]]]\n[[File:Ambanad Hills.jpg|thumb|right|[[Ambanad Hills]] in [[Kollam district]]]]\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Place\n! District\n\n|-\n| [[Achenkovil]]\n| Pathnamthitta\n\n|-\n| [[Agali mandal|Agali]]\n| Palakkad\n\n|-\n| [[Agasthiyamalai]]\n| Thiruvanathapuram\n\n|-\n| [[Ambanad Hills]]\n| Kollam\n\n|-\n| [[Ambalavayal]]\n| Wayanad\n\n|-\n| [[Arimbra Hills, Malappuram]]\n| Malappuram\n\n|-\n| [[Anakkampoyil]]\n| Kozhikode\n\n|-\n| [[Anchuruli]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Aralam]]\n| Kannur\n\n|-\n| [[Anakkara (Idukki)|Anakkara]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Amboori]]\n| Thiruvanathapuram\n\n|-\n| [[Aryankavu]]\n| Kollam\n\n|-\n| [[Athirapally]]\n| Thrissur\n\n|-\n| [[Ayyampuzha]]\n| Ernakulam\n\n|-\n| [[Ayyankunnu]]\n| Wayanad\n\n|-\n| [[Banasura Hill]]\n| Wayanad\n\n|-\n| [[Bison Valley]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Bonacaud]]\n| Thiruvanathapuram\n\n|-\n| [[Brimore]]\n| Thiruvanathapuram\n\n|-\n| [[Chadayamangalam]]\n| Kollam District\n\n|-\n| [[Charalkunnu]]\n| Pathanamthitta\n\n|-\n| [[Chathurangappara]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Cheemeni]]\n| Kasargod\n\n|-\n| [[Chinnakanal]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Chittar, Kerala|Chittar]]\n| Pathanamthitta\n\n|-\n| [[Devikulam]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Dharmathadka]]\n| Kasargod\n\n|-\n| [[Elapeedika]]\n| Kannur\n\n|-\n| [[Elappara]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Ezhimala]]\n| Kannur\n\n|-\n| [[Gavi, Kerala|Gavi]]\n| Pathanamthitta\n \n|-\n| [[Ilaveezha Poonchira]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Illikkal Kallu]]\n| Kotayam\n\n|-\n| [[Iritty]]\n| Kannur\n\n|-\n| [[Kakkadampoyil]]\n| Kozhikode\n\n|-\n| [[Kallar, Trivandrum|Kallar]]\n| Thiruvanathapuram\n\n|-\n| [[Kalpetta]]\n| Wayanad\n\n|-\n| [[Kambilikandam]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Kanthalloor]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Karapuzha Dam]]\n| Wayanad\n\n|-\n| [[Kattappana]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Kinnakorai]]\n| Palakkad\n\n|-\n| [[Kulamavu Dam]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Kulathupuzha]]\n| [[Kollam\n\n|-\n| [[Kodanad]]\n| Ernakulam\n\n|-\n| [[Kodencheri]]\n| Kozhikode\n\n|-\n| [[Kodikuthimala]]\n| Malappuram\n\n|-\n| [[Konni, Pathanamthitta|Konni]]\n| Pathnamthitta\n\n|-\n| [[Koorachundu]]\n| Kozhikode\n\n|-\n| [[Kottancheri Hills]]\n| Kasaragod\n\n|-\n| [[Kottiyoor]]\n| Kannur District\n\n|-\n| [[Kulathupuzha]]\n| Kollam\n\n|-\n| [[Kumily]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Kuttampuzha]]\n| Ernakulam\n|-\n| [[Kuttikkanam]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Lakkidi, Wayanad|Lakkidi]]\n| Wayanad\n\n|-\n| [[Madayipara]]\n| Kannur\n\n|-\n| [[Malakkappara]]\n| Thrissur\n\n|-\n| [[Malayattur]]\n| Ernakulam\n\n|-\n| [[Malom]]\n| Kasargod\n\n|-\n| [[Mananthavady]]\n| Wayanad\n\n|-\n| [[Maniyar]]\n| Pathanamthitta\n\n|-\n| [[Marayoor]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Melukavu]]\n| Kotayam\n\n|-\n| [[Meppadi]]\n| Wayanad\n\n|-\n| [[Moolamattom]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Mundakayam]]\n| Kottayam\n\n|-\n| [[Munnar]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Muthanga]]\n| Wayanad\n\n|-\n| [[Nedumkandam]]\n| Idukki District\n\n|-\n| [[Nelliampathi]]\n| Palakkad\n\n|-\n| [[Padavayal]]\n| Palakkad\n\n|-\n| [[Painavu]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Pakshi Pathalam]]\n| Wayanad\n\n|-\n| [[Panchalimedu]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Parambikulam]]\n| Palakkad\n\n|-\n| [[Parunthumpara]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Pathanamthitta]]\n| Pathanamthitta\n\n|-\n| [[Peermade]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Peruvannamuzhi]]\n| Kozhikode\n\n|-\n| [[Ponmudi]]\n| Thiruvananthapuram\n\n|-\n| [[Poomala]]\n| Thrissur\n\n|-\n| [[Poonjar]]\n| Kottayam\n\n|-\n| [[Ramakkalmedu]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Ranipuram]]\n| Kasaragod\n\n|-\n| [[Ranni]]\n| Pathnamthitta\n\n|-\n| [[Santhanpara]]\n| Idukki District\n\n|-\n| [[Seethathode]]\n| Pathanamthitta\n\n|-\n| [[Soordelu Hill Station]]\n| Kasargod\n\n|-\n| [[Sulthan Bathery]]\n| Wayanad\n\n|-\n| [[Suryanelli]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Teekoy]]\n| Kotayam\n\n|-\n| [[Thamarassery]]\n| Kozhikode\n|-\n| [[Thattekkad]]\n| Ernakulam\n\n|-\n| [[Thekkady]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Thenmala]]\n| Kollam\n\n|-\n| [[Thiruvambadi]]\n| Kozhikode\n\n|-\n| [[Thodupuzha]]\n| Idukki District\n\n|-\n| [[Tirunelli]]\n| Wayanad\n\n|-\n| [[Udumbanchola]]\n| Idukki\n|-\n| [[Vagamon]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Vaithalmala]]\n| Kannur\n\n|-\n| [[Vandiperiyar]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Vaduvanchal]]\n| Wayanad\n\n|-\n| [[Vandanmedu]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Vattavada]]\n| Idukki\n\n|-\n| [[Vazhachal]]\n| Thrissur\n\n|-\n| [[Vazhichal]]\n| Thiruvanathapuram\n\n|-\n| [[Vellarimala]]\n| Kozhikode\n\n|-\n| [[Vithura]]\n| Thiruvananthapuram\n\n|-\n| [[Vythiri]]\n| Wayanad\n\n|}\n\n==Ladakh==\n[[File:Kargil Town as sen from Petrol Pump.jpg|thumb|Kargil Town]]\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Place\n! District\n\n|-\n| [[Dras]]s\n| Kargil\n\n|-\n| [[Kargil]]\n| Kargil\n\n|-\n| [[Leh]]\n| Leh\n\n|}\n\n==Madhya Pradesh==\n\n[[File:Pachmarhi.jpg|thumb|Pandav Caves Pachmarhi]]\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Place\n! District\n\n|-\n| [[Amarkantak]]\n| Anuppur\n\n|-\n| [[Pachmarhi]]\n| Hoshangabad\n\n|}\n\n==Maharashtra==\n\n[[File:Lonavalamh.jpg|thumb|[[Lonavla]], Maharashtra]]\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Place\n! District\n\n|-\n| [[Amboli, Sindhudurg district|Amboli]]\n| Sindhudurg\n\n|-\n| [[Bhandardara]]\n| Ahmednagar\n\n|-\n| [[Chikhaldara]]\n| Amravati\n\n|-\n| [[Igatpuri]]\n| Nashik\n\n|-\n| [[Jawhar]]\n| Palghar\n\n|-\n| [[Karjat]]\n| Raigad\n|-\n| [[Karnala Fort]]\n| Raigad\n\n|-\n| [[Khandala]]\n| Pune\n\n|-\n| [[Lavasa]]\n| Pune\n\n|-\n| [[Lonavala]]\n| Pune\n\n|-\n| [[Mahabaleshwar]]\n| Satara\n\n|-\n| [[Malshej Ghat]]\n| Thane and Ahmednagar\n\n|-